00:29:28.880 --> 00:29:32.768 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:29:32.768 --> 00:29:40.070 align:middle line:90%


00:29:40.070 --> 00:29:43.670 align:middle line:84%
>> Family from Carmel,
their 12-year-old son was

00:29:43.670 --> 00:29:45.190 align:middle line:90%
schizophrenic.

00:29:45.190 --> 00:29:50.089 align:middle line:84%
And his father, a doctor,
called me and was crying.

00:29:50.089 --> 00:29:51.130 align:middle line:90%
And I said, what's wrong?

00:29:51.130 --> 00:29:53.470 align:middle line:90%
He said, my son.

00:29:53.470 --> 00:29:55.510 align:middle line:84%
I've just been told
by his psychiatrist

00:29:55.510 --> 00:29:59.430 align:middle line:84%
that he will never get
well, never get well.

00:29:59.430 --> 00:30:02.881 align:middle line:84%
And so when he was given
that horrible news,

00:30:02.881 --> 00:30:05.380 align:middle line:84%
he began to spend as much time
as they could in the library.

00:30:05.380 --> 00:30:09.880 align:middle line:84%
He ran across the first paper
we ever published in 1957 where

00:30:09.880 --> 00:30:11.500 align:middle line:84%
we first described
the use of vitamins

00:30:11.500 --> 00:30:15.160 align:middle line:84%
for the treatment
of schizophrenia.

00:30:15.160 --> 00:30:18.940 align:middle line:84%
I said, get a hold of some
niacin, and talk to his doctor.

00:30:18.940 --> 00:30:20.820 align:middle line:84%
Maybe he will agree
to put him on it.

00:30:20.820 --> 00:30:23.020 align:middle line:84%
I said to the son's
doctor, would you

00:30:23.020 --> 00:30:25.149 align:middle line:90%
please try this niacin?

00:30:25.149 --> 00:30:26.440 align:middle line:90%
Told him what he knew about it.

00:30:26.440 --> 00:30:29.590 align:middle line:84%
The doctor was very
annoyed, very hostile.

00:30:29.590 --> 00:30:31.110 align:middle line:84%
And he immediately
issued two lies.

00:30:31.110 --> 00:30:34.150 align:middle line:84%
He said, first of all,
it'll fry his brain.

00:30:34.150 --> 00:30:36.550 align:middle line:84%
Then he said, secondly,
we have tried.

00:30:36.550 --> 00:30:37.780 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't work.

00:30:37.780 --> 00:30:39.020 align:middle line:84%
If they had tried it,
and it didn't work,

00:30:39.020 --> 00:30:40.180 align:middle line:90%
why didn't they publish it?

00:30:40.180 --> 00:30:41.680 align:middle line:84%
There was never a
single publication

00:30:41.680 --> 00:30:43.570 align:middle line:90%
from them saying it didn't work.

00:30:43.570 --> 00:30:45.372 align:middle line:90%
They never tried it.

00:30:45.372 --> 00:30:49.836 align:middle line:90%
