00:32:04.839 --> 00:32:05.880 align:middle line:90%
Where did these 1,000 go?

00:32:05.880 --> 00:32:07.450 align:middle line:90%
They went onto the streets.

00:32:07.450 --> 00:32:09.930 align:middle line:84%
They went into
terrible nursing homes.

00:32:09.930 --> 00:32:14.070 align:middle line:84%
They went into terribly
undesirable places.

00:32:14.070 --> 00:32:16.500 align:middle line:84%
>> Once you have schizophrenia,
