00:34:22.310 --> 00:34:24.080 align:middle line:90%
their lifestyle.

00:34:24.080 --> 00:34:27.469 align:middle line:84%
And also when you find out
that it's relatively easy

00:34:27.469 --> 00:34:31.580 align:middle line:84%
to get someone to take a pill,
but to change a behavior is

00:34:31.580 --> 00:34:35.540 align:middle line:84%
